<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
    {{ order.orderCustomer.salutation.letterName }} {{ order.orderCustomer.firstName }} {{ order.orderCustomer.lastName }},<br>
    <br>
    {% if returnLabelDocuments|length  > 1 %}
        Attached to this e-mail you will find {{ returnLabelDocuments|length }} shipping label from DPD for returning
        your order with the number {{ order.orderNumber }}.<br>
        Please print them out and use them to claim the free return shipment.<br>
        Several return labels have been sent to you, as you may need to split your return into several packages to
        comply with DPD's weight limit (20 kg).<br>
    {% else %}
        Attached to this e-mail you will find a shipping label from DPD for returning your order with the number {{ order.orderNumber }}.<br>
        Please print it out and use it to claim the free return shipment.<br>
        We wish you a pleasant day.<br>
    {%  endif %}
    <br>
    Your team from {{ shopName }}.
</div>
